<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
The nine Nazgul, also known as Ringwraiths or Morgul beings, are Sauron’s most dreaded servants.  They are also much dreaded among players, as special precautions must usually be taken when fighting them.  Since they are wraiths, they all appear as black “W”s. <br>
<br>
 <hr>
